ACTION:
With the battery inserted and PSU LED ON, measure the voltage directly at the battery terminals, then at the PSU’s internal 12V output node (where the output cable attaches) relative to the internal 0V node. Verify that a full 12 V is present at the output node and check for any unexpected series resistance or open circuit between the battery positive and the 12V output connection.
